The Shayzien boots (1) are boots that require 20 Defence to equip, and are part of the Shayzien armour (tier 1) set. In order to receive the armour, players must have at least 60% Shayzien favour.

They are dropped by the tier 1 soldier at the Combat Ring in the Shayzien Encampment.
